From the - from the shop, a little old shop you know as we used to go to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13654199\charrsid15081468 Ha'penny}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468  tea and sugar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 How much was that? Would that last a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Oh - yes, it was
 fair you know, only used to be that shop and - as used to do it, little old shop. And - we'd go - perhaps spend a penny and we should have three or four - lots of things for that penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Did you ever go out with just your father, you'd go out with you
r dad when you were helping him sell rabbits and what not and you would go with your dad to visit your gran?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Oh yes, me dad. Me dad used to take us out sometimes.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Visiting relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Yes.
