\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 No. We used to go - never on holidays - we used to go with the Sunday school to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13654199\charrsid15081468 Congleton}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 , like school treats you know - what we used to call Band of Hope 
