to say, tell your mother you've done this and tell your mother you've done that. But - I don't think we really confided in - we did do little things as we said like - you haven't got to tell about you know. But we didn't - confide in 'em like - secretly y
ou know, 'cos they would let it out in the end you know, some of us would. Let it out in the end.
