\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Oh yes, and fly and - hiding seek and - putting cartoons on folks' windows and pulling 'em and all
 that you know, we'd get up to all tricks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 So it would be these kind of games that didn't need much equipment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Yes.
