\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 When - see - s
ometime when we had - we used to have meals at school like, I think it was - when there was some strike on or something we used to have dinners at school.
