Well they were well disciplined you see then. Some of them were - I mean they weren't all you know. Some of 'em - could be naughty I suppose. But - they said we used to do the things they used do today in our days. We used to do thing but we were never - 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13654199\charrsid15081468 doing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468  anything like this, breaking in or anything like that or - we used to - how do you call it - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
