\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Did your parents show any interest in your schoolwork? Would they go up to school?
