\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14299416 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 So it was a neighbourhood school, it drew on all the kids?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Yes.
