\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4343364 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16325461\charrsid15081468 Well I don't think so. Not - if they behave theirselves they didn't. As I say, if you
 were dirty and they weren't tidy they used to pull 'em out of the classroom and send 'em home see. But - I don't think they - in my opinion I don't think they picked on 'em you know, not - personally. We were all the same I think you know, if you - did a
n
ything you got punished and if you - see, if you didn't do your work properly at school you'd have to do it over again, or keep writing on the blackboard. See they - but if you - you go to be tidy. I mean - if you're poor you've got to be clean, they didn
't just - pick on you 'cos you was poor. But you got to be clean.
